1-02-08T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"講景點做假<br />\n<br />\n拍馬都都及不上支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ee6c8f3cbb7025aa1a4700819ae1c075deba8","tid":2399352,"uid":59328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59c0db60aa5a9b4d2bf88fc708ef9f26dea17413","tid":2399352,"uid":69746,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"你整個一模一樣嘅出黎我咪信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"係minecraft整"},{"pid":"31b79ce9060dfe9652b481696c139d5c3748233a","tid":2399352,"uid":59328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3e16775d824fc763e6e620ee21aa36c1e4ce0069","tid":2399352,"uid":89184,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"佢個名已經講緊大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"黃河 清"},{"pid":"f6624a7d368cdcb929f6b6a33498f3de89b9bb12","tid":2399352,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a2808dfe7d95fa5fff6234d1ee625d95596d94a8","tid":2399352,"uid":28114,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"仲鳩噏過連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"嚟緊幾年後考DSE歷史科目嘅學生可以準備背定呢段「史實」喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f721934309890ae23399554bcd419938c2482127","tid":2399352,"uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"係你自己拆撚哂自己的歷史文物啫傻西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aead333f7477291ad23e3c2af3012ea98dd0d0b2","tid":2399352,"uid":91833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"227a4d5715761d92635702b56307887966dd7344","tid":2399352,"uid":220942,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"如果講景點造假<br />\n某國大部份&ldquo;古舊&rdquo;景點都係近十年廿年內起好<br />\n全部都係20世紀人工化<br />\n啤膠，灌紅毛泥咁起<br />\n地點方便旅遊車，一車車咁車啲水魚入去<br />\n<br />\n而相反日本既寺廟，鳥居，就算係翻新，都用番天然木材去翻新"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:26:34.000Z","msg":"忒修斯之船（英語：ship of Theseus），亦稱忒修斯悖論，是形而上學領域內關於同一性的一種悖論。 1世紀時的希臘作家普魯塔克提出了這個問題：如果忒修斯的船上的木頭逐漸被替換，直到所有的木頭都不是原來的木頭，那這艘船還是原來的那艘船嗎？ 這類問題現在被稱做「忒修斯之船」。"},{"pid":"71880ae3e33d0c1dca820a95fb96d56701a6be80","tid":2399352,"uid":165136,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"唔係偽造古代遺跡<br />\n埃及同雅典自古以來都係中國領土<br />\n睇壁畫D人都係黑頭髮, 黑眼睛, 黃皮膚<br />\n有時係淺D 嘅黑頭髮黑眼睛, 有時係深D 嘅黃皮膚<br />\n但好明顯頭髮, 黑眼睛, 黃皮膚係中國人<br />\n中國人的事能叫偽造嗎?"},{"pid":"2212a845faa366399261c4538ea212cc56f98a7a","tid":2399352,"uid":128705,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:28:42.000Z","msg":"班支那佬成日用自己套「耐就係好」既思維去套落人地果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就不斷FF自己有幾老 文化源遠流長<br />\n仲唔抵得人地都有差唔多咁耐既歷史<br />\n就去屈人地係假 係人地偷自己野 自己先係正宗乜乜乜 鬥臭人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd20b9eb190dc306e07bbf44f2c6989d40427ef","tid":2399352,"uid":335434,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"59c0db60aa5a9b4d2bf88fc708ef9f26dea17413","tid":2399352,"uid":69746,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"你整個一模一樣嘅出黎我咪信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4WCnLh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4WCnLh.jpg&h=e8ecb40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWcRsbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu